<script>
    import configuratorAPI from '@/configurator/configuratorAPI'
    import sketchfabdata from '@/data/sketchfabdata'

    export default {
        name: 'player',
        components: {},
        props: {},
        computed: {},
        methods: {
            loadScene () {
                const sceneui = sketchfabdata.sceneuid.production;
                //const sceneui = sketchfabdata.sceneuid.development;
                configuratorAPI.load(sceneui, sketchfabdata.playersettings).then(api => {
                    console.log('ready');
                })
            },
        },
        mounted () {
            this.loadScene()
        }
    }
</script>


<template>
    <iframe
        id="player__iframe"
        class="player"/>
</template>


<style lang="scss">
    @import '@/styles/variables.scss';

    .player {
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: 50% 50%;
    }
</style>
